title: James Reserve station migration
description: James wx station logger moved to new enclosure on the tower, temp/rh, anemometer,  RAD, PAR, soil moisture probes are new sensors. Anemometer is now a 05103 turbine  unit, mounted at top of the tower. A thermocouple was added in a gill shield at 9.5  meters. PAR sensor replaced with like, RAD sensor replaced with Li200. Soil moisture  probed replaced with CS616's. Temp/humidity sensor replaced with HMP60. Logger  power now has battery backup, communications now via NL116 incident report migrated from SensorDB.

external_refs.identifier: James Reserve station migration; see incident report IR_467
